  Autumn Villas – San Bernardino









 







Autumn Villas
San Bernardino, CA

Autumn Villas at University Park is an exquisite housing development by Maple Ventures IV, LLC. This development will feature 64-single family homes within a private development located directly across the street from Cal State San Bernardino. This infill project will feature three individual two-story homes ranging from 1740 sq. ft. to 1950 sq.ft. This project will have a small Home Owner’s Association (HOA) to manage the site, along with the common landscaping that surrounds the homes, and the park facing Northpark Boulevard. 
For more information click here













