  Yucaipa









 







Autumn Terrace
Yucaipa, CA
33 SFR under construction at the corner of 3rd Street and Bella Vista Drive in Yucaipa, CA.  Homes will range from 4 bedrooms with 3 baths to 4 bedrooms 3 baths. 2350 sq. ft. to 2700 sq. ft.
Closing of last homes expected Winter 2016.

For more information click here














Autumn Crossings
Yucaipa, CA
33 SFR to be under construction in October 2015. Located on 5th Street in Yucaipa, CA. Homes will range from 3 to 5 bedrooms and 2.5 to 3 bathrooms. 2248 sq. ft. to 2796 sq. ft.












