  Idaho









 







Post Falls, Idaho
 
Post Falls, Idaho, is a mixed-use development located between Coeur d’Alene, Idaho and metropolitan Spokane, Washington. This development includes retail, hospitality, industrial, office, and residential opportunities. Lots range from under one acre to over 100 acres. Existing uses include: light industrial, gas stations, fast food and a surgical center. Currently available property totals approximately 225 acres. For more information on available properties, please click HERE.












